org.pepstock.charba.client.commons

Class NativeExtendedObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeExtendedObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ScriptableContext

    @JsType(isNative=true,
        name="Object",
        namespace="<global>")
public abstract class NativeExtendedObject
extends Object
    Base native object which can be extended by native object where additional properties could be needed, added as java script object into a property called 'options'.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
